api_list.api_description: Get browser, OS, and device information by parsing a user-agent string.

required_parameters.name: ua
required_parameters.description: The user-agent string to be parsed.
required_parameters.default: Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_15_5) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/89.0.4389.114 Safari/537.36

query: What browser, OS, and device information can you provide me from this user-agent string: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_15_5) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/89.0.4389.114 Safari/537.36'?
